Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:04.15,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Today is the day, Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.82,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can just feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:10.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Today is the day we are all gonna\Nget our cutie marks in…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:12.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…bowlin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.77,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I mean… Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:23.17,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Why, after today we won't even be the Cutie Mark Crusaders anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We'll be the…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.07,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…the Three Strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.52,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That makes us sound\Nlike we've struck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.79,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,How about… the Pin Twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.59,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But there are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.11,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,The Bowling Dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,The Bowling Dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.04,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:47.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Alrighty then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Let's bowl 'em over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! A bowling cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.61,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.80,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But what about my ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That bowling sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.68,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Even if all I got was gutterballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:45.18,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At least you're able to keep your ball in your lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.53,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I don't think Mr. Kingpin is ever\Ngonna let me play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.10,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Hey! Maybe I could get\Nmy cutie mark in demolition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.84,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.68,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I know just what you need to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,put the bloom back on your apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.30,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,A treat from Sugarcube Corner will cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.56,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A party will cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,A lovely new chapeau will cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No, it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.68,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Come on, Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.16,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,It's just a cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.45,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Or lack of a cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.32,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Shh! That's not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.97,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.41,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.32,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.13,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Well. Who is it that we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.83,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Why, it's Apple Bloom, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.68,Zecora,,0,0,0,,What has happened to you, youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.17,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Ah, you've gone and chipped your tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.84,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Come with me. I have just the trick…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.16,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…that will fix you up quite quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.37,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I tried everything, Thecora.\NAnd thtill no cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm gonna be as old as Granny Thmith
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.66,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,and thtill have a blank flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.63,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Your frustration is well understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.62,Zecora,,0,0,0,,But one must be patient for all things good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I've heard that from everypony I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.32,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And now from every Thebra I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm jutht too impathient to be pathient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.18,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I jutht want my cutie mark and I want it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.69,Zecora,,0,0,0,,For your cutie mark you will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.56,Zecora,,0,0,0,,We must fix that tooth before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.88,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Now drink down every little drop…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.46,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…and this mixture will mend that chip on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh my star apples! You did it, Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.18,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You have tonics that heal all sorts of ailments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Bad bones, bad back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,bad breath…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.07,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Yes, little one. It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.69,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I have many a healing brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.32,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And not only stuff that fixes the bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.35,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…but stuff that brings the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.39,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Good health, good hair…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,good heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.80,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I bet you can mix up a brew to fix…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.82,Zecora,,0,0,0,,There are many mixtures in this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.95,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…but none for what you want, dear Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.04,Zecora,,0,0,0,,A magic potion does not hold the key…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.12,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…for a cutie mark. Time is the only remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What's you got goin' on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:20.16,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I am brewing up another mix for a rooster and his chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.41,Zecora,,0,0,0,,It seems the rooster has lost his crow…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:25.00,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…making mornings very slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:27.95,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hey! I've seen that flower bloomin' in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:28.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.76,Zecora,,0,0,0,,It is one we call "heart's desire".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.53,Zecora,,0,0,0,,A dash will ignite the rooster's fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:40.01,Zecora,,0,0,0,,With heart's desire his talent comes into view…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.02,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…and he'll make a mighty\Ncock-a-doodle-doo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Zowie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Heart's desire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.48,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Ay me! But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.38,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I've run out of amethyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:58.17,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I must go get this purple flower for my brew to have full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.28,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.18,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! You've got\Nyour cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.06,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.53,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Is it an "O"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.17,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Is your talent spelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.44,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Or is it a ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.02,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Are you\Na jewelery maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or ith it a powdered donut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cauthe that thouhdth delithoiuth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No. It's a loop-de-hoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.74,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,A what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.15,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,A loop-de-hoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.14,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,'least that's what I always called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:56.78,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack made it for my from an old ring barrel when I was littler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought that loop-de-hoop would end up bein' my special talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.59,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wow, Apple Bloom! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.18,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,That's it? That's your talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:09.86,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Spinning a hoop around\Nyour waist? Puh-lease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:13.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh. You ain't seen nothin' yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.63,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.27,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,You're super-duper loop-de-hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.78,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.67,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,All right, my little ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.20,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Time for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.73,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yes, miss Cheerilee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.64,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,I want you to take your loop-de-hoop into the yard…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:57.41,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,…and give us all a lesson in your amazing loop-de-hooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, gals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.86,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Keep at it and you --\Nmight get to be half as good as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Great job, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You're too kind, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.35,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Nah. You just need a little practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.17,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Soon you'll be able to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hoop'n'bob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hoop'n'hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hoop'n'skip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And hoop'n'flip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.89,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Show us some more, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.30,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just a few\Nmore tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But be warned…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…these are advanced moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Not for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Got that, Diamond Tiara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:13.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I call this one the hoop-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:34.95,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Another cutie mark? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:38.18,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I guess that last trick was a lot of hoop-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.89,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Those cutie marks are fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What? No, they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.28,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Miss Cheerilee,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:48.73,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,have you ever heard of a pony with two cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.67,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,I must say that I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.01,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,But maybe Apple Bloom\Nhas two special talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.89,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.22,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Then let's see you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.90,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Two cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Two talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.74,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Our friend is the most special pony ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Alright, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You ready for a real show?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw, little sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Huh, congratulations on gettin' not just one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but two cutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:37.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're mighty proud of you. Right, Big McIntosh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.00,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anythin' like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Have you, Big Mac?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:43.88,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Nnope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:48.75,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Why, the way you were a-hoopin' and\Na-hoppin' and kickin' and spinnin'…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:51.95,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,…reminded me of when I was a spry young filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.99,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Charlie horse! Charlie horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.69,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:03.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Why, Apple Bloom. I think you're ready to hit the rodeo circuit right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm ready to hit the hay right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm plum tucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'll see y'all in the mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:11.76,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,'night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,'night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Little Apple Bloom has finally blossomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hasn't she, Big Mac?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.84,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Eeyep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom. What is all that awful…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:39.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,…tapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Three cutie marks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.18,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come 'ere, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.07,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.85,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, I know somepony who might.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Three cutie marks? Three talents!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was just reading something about unusual equine illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Perplexing Pony Plagues", perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, Spike! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I do have some talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:40.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hay fever… the trots…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cutie pox!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie pox?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cutie pox – this puzzling\Npony plague afflicted…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…the population of ponies back in the paleopony period!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Say that ten times fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Random cutie marks appeared all over the ponies' bodies…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…causing them to perform all the talents that came with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:02.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yes, but what's the cure? What's the cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It says here there's no known cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No known cure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The cause of the breakout was never discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And the cutie pox disappeared as mysteriously as they arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.78,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sacré bleu! Plus de marque de cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Qu'est-ce que c'est? Je parle français?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My sister's speakin' in Fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:33.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know she needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We can't just wait for this to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We gotta find somepony to mix up a cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Tout suite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not somepony. Some zebra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Dépêchez-vous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.59,LillyValley,,0,0,0,,She's cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.63,Rose,,0,0,0,,Hexed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.48,Daisy,,0,0,0,,Enchanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,She just has some weird, mysterious disease\Nwith no known cure, called cutie pox.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,CUTIE POX?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.78,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I thought I have removed their fear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.91,Zecora,,0,0,0,,the last time I visited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.71,Zecora,,0,0,0,,But doors are barred and shutters shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.48,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Guess I should have stayed inside my hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom has cutie pox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We were just on our way\Nto see if you've had a cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But magically you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Was your zebra sense a-tinglin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.62,Zecora,,0,0,0,,My zebra sense did not bring me 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.34,Zecora,,0,0,0,,It was a special flower that I needed found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.88,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd picked enough to fix all the potions I had to mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.41,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…but after my visit from Apple Bloom…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:32.41,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…some have mysteriously left my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.60,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.28,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Did this flower just walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.70,Zecora,,0,0,0,,A cutie pox cure I have forsooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.20,Zecora,,0,0,0,,For healing power is in the seeds of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,W… well then. Give 'em to her! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.72,Zecora,,0,0,0,,These seeds must be planted in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.34,Zecora,,0,0,0,,With the truth they'll grow and the cure is found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.42,Zecora,,0,0,0,,The seeds of truth do hold the cure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.21,Zecora,,0,0,0,,but one must speak words…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.90,Zecora,,0,0,0,,…true and pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright. They're planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now somepony tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Somepony! Anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yesterday I told Mrs. Cake\Nthat I ate two corn cakes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,…but I really ate three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay, six!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I ate six corn cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Make it stop! Oh, make it stop!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's me! I admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.25,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I didn't earn my cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.71,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,They're all fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I figured the heart's desire would help me get what I wanted most…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…so when Zecora left her hut,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mixed up a special potion…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,…and put the rest of the heart's desire in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.97,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.30,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And I've never been happier to be a blank flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.10,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But I'm awful sorry I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Especially to you, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I was so desperate for my cutie mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I just got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.99,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And I'm really sorry I snuck those flowers from you, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Why, I wouldn't blame you if you never wanted me to come by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.71,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Now, Apple Bloom. Do not be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.12,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You are always welcome, my little filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:18.33,Zecora,,0,0,0,,With each mistake you learn something new,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:21.03,Zecora,,0,0,0,,growing up into a better you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,would you mind writing to Princess Celestia…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…and telling her what you learned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:31.07,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dear Princess Celestia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:38.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for what your heart desires can be really hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.35,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you may try to take a shortcut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this dishonesty never works,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:45.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because you didn't earn what your heart desires.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:48.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only cure is being honest with yourself and others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's something every heart desires."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I sure am proud of you, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:59.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Seems like you've finally learned the importance of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.63,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:03.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,All good things come to those who wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.88,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, I've waited long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.72,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Actually, that was way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:12.46,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,So what are we gonna do today to earn our cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:16.95,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Well, I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.30,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,For a pony, who's never mixed up a potion before…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.35,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,…you sure stirred up something fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yeah! So what if your talent is potion making?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:26.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Let's go talk to Zecora! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:29.55,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONEC
